import { Button, Col, Form, Row } from "react-bootstrap";
import React from "react";

function ProfileDetails() {
  return (
    <Form className="text-center p-2 w-50">
      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="Name">
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">
          FirstName
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm="4">
          <Form.Control 
            name="firstName"
            type="text" 
            placeholder="First Name" 
          />
        </Col>
        <Form.Label 
          column 
          className="sr-only">
          LastName
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm="6">
          <Form.Control 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="Last Name" 
          />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="title">
        <Form.Label
          column 
          className="sr-only"
        >
          Title
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm="12">
          <Form.Control 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="Title" 
          />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="company"> 
        <Form.Label 
          column 
          className="sr-only"
        >
          Company
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm="12">
          <Form.Control 
            plaintext 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="Company" 
          />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="location">
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">
          City
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm="4">
          <Form.Control 
            plaintext 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="City" 
          />
        </Col>
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">
          Country
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm="6">
          <Form.Control 
            plaintext 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="Country" 
          />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>

      <Button 
       type="submit">
        Save
      </Button>
    </Form>
  );
}

export default ProfileDetails;
